        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 5 at 11:22AM CDT until June 5 at 12:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 1122 AM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 8 miles northwest
of Codman, or 11 miles northeast of Pampa, moving east at 30 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.
People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles.

Locations impacted include...
Codman, Lora, and Miami.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
